## Technical Patterns

### AI-Enhanced Bookmark Categorization

- **Description**: Using machine learning models to automatically categorize and organize bookmarks based on their content, context, or user behavior.
- **Implementation Notes**: Requires training datasets, natural language processing (NLP) techniques, and integration with the bookmark management system.
